Business Brief -- R.H. Macy  Co.:
   Bankruptcy Trustee Picks
   Representatives for Creditors
Those on the bond committee include representatives of
Loomis Sayles  Co., Boston, an investment management
company, and Executive Life Insurance Co., a unit of First
Executive Corp., Los Angeles. The trade committee includes
representatives of Sony Corp., Liz Claiborne Inc., Leslie Fay
Cos. and a local union. The two committees are expected to
appoint professional advisers shortly.